{"tid":1259823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【公信力第柒】投訴明報簡易指南(內附email template)","createTime":"2019-06-26T16:35:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T05:35:56.000Z","uid":11223,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1d13fef7bc0527ae99a635e53299872ad290db4c","tid":1259823,"uid":11223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:35:08.000Z","msg":"請問處理呢篇稿嘅記者同編輯咩事啊？<br />\n咁都俾你諗到真係勁，東方都無你咁叻。對你地好失望。<br />\n而家改咗條題就想扮無事？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[red]]無咁易啊！！！[/red</span><br />\n大家照report同投訴！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEmail: mingpao@mingpao.com<br />\n<br />\nTemplate:<br />\n<br />\n貴「公信力第一」傳媒、明報總編輯：<br />\n<br />\n本人強烈投訴「明報即時新聞」2019年6月26日21:55刊登有關六旬漢死亡報導，　貴「公信力第一」傳媒曾在標題加上涉案者為曾參與遊行人士，內文亦特別加一段強調此事，請問曾參與遊行與推跌老翁的關連為何？此做法與往日各媒體以「疑患精神病」來連結傷人案一樣，是將不一定相關的事情扣上關連，誤導公眾，亦使相關族群被標籤、污名化，何況這次「曾參與遊行」與推跌老翁有何關係？難免令人懷疑　貴「公信力第一」傳媒企圖將「曾參與遊行人士」污名化，亦令人質疑　貴「公信力第一」傳媒之動機，以及是否仍然具有公信力。此做法缺乏傳媒道德操守，請　貴報加以正視，雖現時已更改標題，但仍應在網上及報紙刊登道歉聲明。<br />\n此外，本人身為　貴報多年讀者，深知面對網絡即時新聞世界，需要爭分奪秒，但不代表可以毫無把關，例如是胡亂配上標題及內容、不刊登記者名字，甚至這篇報導，是否記者所寫亦無從得知。如果是管理層或外界勢力干預，讀者亦無從知曉。而報導中的案件，全港各大傳媒的標題及內文都未有如　貴「公信力第一」傳媒般處理（附圖），當其他傳媒都堅守傳媒操守，請　貴報承擔「公信力第一」的責任，切勿為不知名利益而損害報譽。<br />\n本人身為　貴報長期讀者，現已unlike及block了「明報即時新聞」，以免再被　貴報不專業的報導荼毒心靈。現要求　貴報為此事負責：<br />\n1. 在明報即時新聞facebook page及報章刊登獨立的道歉聲明<br />\n2. 在原報導網頁內刊登道歉聲音<br />\n3. 刊出記者／撰稿人名字<br />\n4. 日後的任何新聞均須刊出撰稿人姓名<br />\n5. 檢討即時新聞及其他所有新聞的審核機制<br />\n在　貴報未有詳加檢討及實行以上建議前，本人均不會再點擊、閱讀、購買　貴集團任何文字，亦會呼籲大眾一同抵制　貴報。<br />\n<br />\n不再是讀者<br />\nXXX<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e16807ad0daf1450059a1083b88f017ca418604","tid":1259823,"uid":11223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S5tWTBc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS5tWTBc.png&h=0129d47b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ce2db1f3050bd668abf1372908d9d6cf7dd587f","tid":1259823,"uid":11223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5f24cbc997d1022521ede180c2a81345704793","tid":1259823,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:41:05.000Z","msg":"日月神報，公信第柒"},{"pid":"2d801826bbb961ad610afadbf7df3247477fded3","tid":1259823,"uid":258416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:47:23.000Z","msg":"推，謝樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0ce9f556f34a1c9f4d4fa6375a584df08efa68","tid":1259823,"uid":11223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:49:23.000Z","msg":"推啊！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56553082e7188a90a8576ced3613e7f35ca3ca6","tid":1259823,"uid":11223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0b8091e5a3f11ae4628c5a226b8ecb73486274","tid":1259823,"uid":176714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:53:40.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400d1a13c66b66d0c4720f13e797803fbceb066e","tid":1259823,"uid":270000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:01:31.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ef0b56e0b56dd91277d23d488affcb09e19b32d9","tid":1259823,"uid":11223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:03:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">再嚟！！！！！！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢封係記協！！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nEmail: hkja@hkja.org.hk<br />\n<br />\n您好，<br />\n<br />\n本人強烈投訴「明報即時新聞」2019年6月26日21:55刊登有關六旬漢死亡報導，該報導曾在標題加上涉案者為曾參與遊行人士，內文亦特別加一段強調此事，然而，一個專業的媒體，刻意將兩者扣上關連，與往日各媒體以「疑患精神病」來連結傷人案一樣，是企圖誤導公眾，亦使相關族群被標籤、污名化，何況這次「曾參與遊行」與推跌老翁有何關係？難免令人懷疑該報動機，以及是否仍然有公信力。此做法缺乏傳媒道德操守，雖然該報雖現時已更改標題，但仍懇請　貴會發表聲明，並從不同途徑加以查詢、追究，以正視聽。<br />\n此外，本人深知面對網絡即時新聞世界，需要爭分奪秒，但不代表可以毫無把關，例如是胡亂配上標題及內容、不刊登記者名字，甚至這篇報導，是否記者所寫亦無從得知。如果是管理層或外界勢力干預，讀者亦無從知曉。而報導中的案件，全港各大傳媒的標題及內文都未有如明報般處理（附圖），當其他傳媒都堅守傳媒操守，請　貴會協助維持傳媒的公信力，以免讀者對本地新聞更加失望。<br />\n本人認為該報應為此事負責：<br />\n1. 在明報即時新聞facebook page及報章刊登獨立的道歉聲明<br />\n2. 在原報導網頁內刊登道歉聲音<br />\n3. 刊出記者／撰稿人名字<br />\n4. 日後的任何新聞均須刊出撰稿人姓名<br />\n5. 檢討即時新聞及其他所有新聞的審核機制<br />\n希望　貴會在大義之前，能與讀者共同守護香港。<br />\n<br />\n市民<br />\nXXX<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3489770171798ebeadad53bce084914db61ee9","tid":1259823,"uid":11223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:07:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3257126db5aac6eb11587b46500d077730ff16","tid":1259823,"uid":270000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:11:05.000Z","msg":"比D壓力佢 唔好以為可以間唔中出D咁既新聞黎搞9市民"},{"pid":"13f3328264546641c6cf7fffc25fd73300015525","tid":1259823,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:15:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac228011a8f1419a597a002baab8a59f2c6f709a","tid":1259823,"uid":270000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:15:59.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1029be6bec2b5f0677e2f1db887e77b8a6abfd7d","tid":1259823,"uid":264676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:16:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b29249448d10e66d028d383d03087ea20620462","tid":1259823,"uid":101756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:27:57.000Z","msg":"😡"},{"pid":"87211cf160d89d22b49ec23f7f48b558c413e22c","tid":1259823,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1dec742644beaf0c37dd1eac1e5c35e4cc4d7ee","tid":12